        "message": "Patch Set 6: Verified+1\n\nBuild Successful \n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/cps-master-verify-java/1767/ : SUCCESS\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/cps-master-verify-java/1767\n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/cps-sonar-verify/197/ : SUCCESS\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/cps-sonar-verify/197\n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/cps-review-verification-maven-master/1112/ : SUCCESS\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/cps-review-verification-maven-master/1112",
